dmca.title: Website of Alleged Copyright Infringment Victim is Down
dmca.body:
March 28, 2008
 
Dear Frantech, Veritynet - 

It has come to my attention that you are republishing original content from www.supremel2.com (Sept, 06)on your Website, located at www.supremel2.org. (Mar, 08)

Your unauthorized use of original material from www.supremel2.com is in violation of copyrights owned by www.supremel2.com. If you do not immediately remove the copyrighted material from www.supremel2.org, and notify me in writing that you have done so, I will have no choice but to pursue legal action against you. We require the copyrighted material to be removed and written notice given that such has been removed, by no later than 30 March 2008.
 
Title17, Cingular92, Ch5.504.c.1/.2
 

(c) Statutory Damages.
